<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>You're On The List | Refinery Aesthetics</title>
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300;1,400&family=Jost:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

  <style>
    :root {
      --dark:    #1a1a1a;
      --gold:    #c8a96e;
      --gold-lt: #e2cfa5;
      --cream:   #f0ebe3;
      --white:   #faf8f4;
      --muted:   #7a7168;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    html, body {
      margin: 0 !important;
      padding: 0 !important;
      width: 100% !important;
      max-width: 100% !important;
      overflow-x: hidden !important;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      background: var(--dark);
      color: var(--white);
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .bg-layer {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 55% at 50% -5%,  rgba(200,169,110,0.16) 0%, transparent 65%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 45% at 10% 110%, rgba(200,169,110,0.07) 0%, transparent 55%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 40% at 90% 110%, rgba(200,169,110,0.07) 0%, transparent 55%);
    }

    .page {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 64px 32px 72px;
      text-align: center;
      width: 100vw !important;
      left: 50% !important;
      margin-left: -50vw !important;
    }

    .logo {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
      margin-bottom: 52px;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .logo-word {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(26px, 4vw, 38px);
      font-weight: 300;
      letter-spacing: 0.28em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--white);
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .logo-rule {
      width: 36px;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--gold);
      opacity: 0.65;
      margin: 6px 0;
    }
    .logo-sub {
      font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.45em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    .check {
      width: 56px;
      height: 56px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.5);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 36px;
    }
    .check svg { width: 20px; height: 20px; color: var(--gold); }

    .eyebrow {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.35em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 14px;
    }
    .eyebrow::before, .eyebrow::after {
      content: '';
      display: block;
      width: 28px;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--gold);
      opacity: 0.45;
    }

    .headline {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(42px, 7vw, 68px);
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.05;
      color: var(--white);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }
    .headline em { font-style: italic; color: var(--gold-lt); }

    .subhead {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(18px, 3vw, 24px);
      font-weight: 300;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .rule {
      width: 44px;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--gold);
      opacity: 0.45;
      margin: 0 auto 28px;
    }

    .body-copy {
      font-size: clamp(14px, 1.8vw, 15.5px);
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.9;
      color: rgba(250,248,244,0.72);
      max-width: 400px;
      margin: 0 auto 44px;
    }

    /* Notice box */
    .notice-box {
      max-width: 420px;
      margin: 0 auto 48px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.2);
      padding: 28px 32px;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .notice-label {
      font-size: 9px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      display: block;
    }

    .notice-box p {
      font-size: 13.5px;
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.85;
      color: rgba(250,248,244,0.6);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .notice-box p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

    /* What to expect */
    .expect-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: baseline;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .expect-row:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

    .expect-num {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 300;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--gold);
      flex-shrink: 0;
      width: 20px;
    }

    .expect-text {
      font-size: 13.5px;
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: rgba(250,248,244,0.6);
    }

    .btn-outline {
      display: inline-block;
      border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.45);
      color: var(--gold);
      padding: 13px 36px;
      font-family: 'Jost', sans-serif;
      font-size: 10.5px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: border-color 0.25s, background 0.25s, color 0.25s;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }
    .btn-outline:hover {
      background: var(--gold);
      border-color: var(--gold);
      color: var(--dark);
    }

    .social {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }
    .social a {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.22);
      border-radius: 50%;
      color: rgba(250,248,244,0.30);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    }
    .social a:hover { border-color: rgba(200,169,110,0.55); color: var(--gold); }

    .copyright {
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: rgba(250,248,244,0.2);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(18px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    .logo       { animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.1s  both; }
    .check      { animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease 0.2s  both; }
    .eyebrow    { animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease 0.28s both; }
    .headline   { animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease 0.35s both; }
    .subhead    { animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.42s both; }
    .rule       { animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease 0.48s both; }
    .body-copy  { animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.54s both; }
    .notice-box { animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease 0.62s both; }
    .btn-outline { animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease 0.70s both; }
    .social     { animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease 0.76s both; }

    @media (max-width: 500px) {
      .page { padding: 48px 24px 60px; }
      .notice-box { padding: 24px 22px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="bg-layer"></div>

  <div class="page">

    <a href="https://www.refineryaestheticswi.com" class="logo">
      <span class="logo-word">Refinery</span>
      <div class="logo-rule"></div>
      <span class="logo-sub">Aesthetics</span>
    </a>

    <div class="check">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
        <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <p class="eyebrow">RSVP Received</p>
    <h1 class="headline">You're on<br><em>the list.</em></h1>
    <p class="subhead">We can't wait to meet you.</p>
    <div class="rule"></div>

    <p class="body-copy">Your spot is noted. The date is still being confirmed between your host and our team, but you'll be the first to know once everything is locked in.</p>

    <div class="notice-box">
      <span class="notice-label">A few things to know</span>
      <div class="expect-row">
        <span class="expect-num">01</span>
        <span class="expect-text">The party date is pending confirmation. Your host is working with us to finalize the details.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="expect-row">
        <span class="expect-num">02</span>
        <span class="expect-text">Once confirmed you'll receive a follow-up with everything you need to know before the event.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="expect-row">
        <span class="expect-num">03</span>
        <span class="expect-text">In the meantime, follow us on Instagram to get a feel for what Refinery is all about.</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <a href="https://www.refineryaestheticswi.com" class="btn-outline">Explore Refinery Aesthetics</a>

    <div class="social">
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/refineryaestheticswi" aria-label="Instagram" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5"/>
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"/>
          <circle cx="17.5" cy="6.5" r="1" fill="currentColor" stroke="none"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a href="https://www.facebook.com/RefineryAestheticsWI" aria-label="Facebook" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>

    <p class="copyright">© 2026 Refinery Aesthetics &nbsp;·&nbsp; Bancroft, WI</p>

  </div>

  <script>
    function sendHeight() {
      var h = document.documentElement.scrollHeight;
      window.parent.postMessage({ type: 'resize', id: 'refinery-rsvp-thankyou', height: h }, '*');
    }
    if (window.ResizeObserver) new ResizeObserver(sendHeight).observe(document.body);
    window.addEventListener('load', sendHeight);
    window.addEventListener('resize', sendHeight);
    sendHeight();
  </script>

</body>
</html>
